f0cb8","tid":482231,"uid":2762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今年年頭Logan幾好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLOGAN真係好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終佢唔係主sell救世界既野 <br />\n純粹講一個英雄既沒落 反而更有英雄感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFOX試緊唔同野，Deadpool 唔算好好睇，不過好有趣。佢地新個一套The New Mutants 又好似同一貫玩法唔同，18年上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得Fox起碼係有理解個角色/作品先 雖然唔係套套都話好好睇"},{"pid":"b557ca5bd6e56288ba6cd367a569454727fe66be","tid":482231,"uid":143572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T04:22:10.000Z","msg":"好多分析都話infinity war 會係super hero movie 既轉捩點, 而家幾間studio 一年夾埋7-10 套。大部分都係票房保證, 但打完大佬, 成個MCU 要多幾個phases 先再build up 個universe 新大佬, 講梗都超過十年。個trend 都會因咁冷卻。<br />\n<br />\n而Fox 雖然DP/LOGAN 都叫好叫座, 新X MEN series都唔差, 係新F4 7 到喊。但佢地一直都係偏向獨立故事, 好難好似MCU 咁帶番起個trend。可能DISNEY 搞得掂Fox 可以玩AVENGER VS XMEN, 但暫時都冇乜聲氣。<br />\n<br />\n至於DCEU, WB 管理層唔係傻仔, 個個觀眾覺得DCEU 冇乜獨立英雄故事去build up JL, 相信管理層唔係唔知, 但係一個phases 少則都3年, WB 又偏向搵big name, big cast。(MCU 起初專搵D 半紅不黑) 成本高, 又怕回報期太耐。結果, 係英雄片條水仲有得食, 一口氣出左BVS JL。WB偏向short依類型既片, 小丑外傳都睇得出WB 唔太打算以DCEU 做單一發展。"},{"pid":"cd3ffe92ccfc151dc4de7b05625f76c42f0e8ef8","tid":482231,"uid":82743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T04:29:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>今年年頭Logan幾好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLOGAN真係好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"